                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for nasf &amp;lt;fan.yong@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/60ca627c-97d7-11e4-ba89-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/60ca627c-97d7-11e4-ba89-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

